title: 820-4924 not turning on
message:
Have 820-4924 with very mild water damage. When it came in it would get orange light on charger but board only draw 0.14 amps from power supply with or without battery.

After replacing Q7520 C7571 C7116 and R7116 the board draws 2.9amps with battery plugged in and only 0.14 without plugged in. Battery is supposedly new. Heatsink gets very warm after few minutes with battery and charger connected but no fan spin.

PPBUS_G3H 12.56v
PP3V42_G3H 3.42v
PPVRTC_G3H 3.33v
PP5V_S5 5.5V

Could this be bad battery or fan?

title: 820-4924 not turning on
message: solved, battery needed to be charged

title: 820-4924 not turning on
message: That is normal behaviour for 4924; fan starts later, when CPU gets really hot...
